    "Id": "vehicledef_MYRMIDON",
    "Name": "Myrmidon Medium Tank",
    "UIName": "Myrmidon Medium Tank (Standard)",
    "Details": "<b>Name: <color=#85DBF6>Myrmidon Medium Tank</color>\nArmor: <color=#85DBF6>Standard</color>\tTechnology: <color=#85DBF6>Inner Sphere</color>\nMovement: <color=#85DBF6>5/8 (Tracked)</color>\tEngine: <color=#85DBF6>200 Fusion</color></b>\n\nThe Myrmidon Medium Tank is a cost-effective alternative to BattleMechs for Chaos March powers. Based on the Manticore, it offers comparable combat capabilities at a lower price, making it attractive to military buyers with limited resources.\n\nThe Myrmidon's primary weapon is a powerful PPC, capable of striking targets from a distance. Its crew often relies on the tank's speed to maintain a safe distance from close-range threats. However, if caught in close combat, the Myrmidon can rely on its SRM-6 launcher for additional firepower. Both weapons are mounted in the turret, allowing for a full range of fire.",
